# Design and Analysis of Algorithms (DAA)

This folder contains the laboratory programs and practical assignments completed as part of the Design and Analysis of Algorithms (DAA) course.

## Contents

- Divide and Conquer Algorithms
- Greedy Algorithms
- Dynamic Programming
- Backtracking
- Branch and Bound
- Graph Algorithms
- Sorting and Searching
- Algorithm Analysis
- Lab Assignments

## Technologies Used

- C++
- Visual Studio Code

## Objective

To understand algorithm design techniques, analyze their time and space complexity, and implement efficient solutions for computational problems.
